<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                            <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>Zirkendorff<ex>er</ex>s,</expan> Bernharts
                            <expan>vom<ex>m</ex></expan> Stein und <expan cert="unknown">C.</expan>
                        Zeͣhen <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und tun
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> zu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz
                                <expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan> drey uns und die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> beschedigt, das ir
                                <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan>, etlich
                            <expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan> und bescheczt
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> on schuld und on sache; wie
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>, so <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir das umb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> in gut <add>gen in</add> ansteen
                                <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>hiezwische<ex>n</ex></expan>
<app>
<note><q type="date"><expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>heilig<ex>en</ex></expan> tag</q>01.11.1420</note>
</app> schierist <expan>kom<ex>m</ex>end</expan>, also daz sie in
                                <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan> zeit zu uns gen
                                <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
<expan>kom<ex>m</ex>e<ex>n</ex></expan>, so <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir in zu und von uns für uns und die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on
                                <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan> und bey uns für
                                <expan>all<ex>er</ex>menikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> iiii tag geleyt
                                <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und ir rede
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan>. <pb facs="#facs_172" id="85r"/>
<expan>Well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sie das also
                        <expan>aufneme<ex>n</ex></expan>, so laszt uns des ewr
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir uns darnach
                            <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>zu richte<ex>n</ex></expan>. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Mathei <expan>app<ex>osto</ex>li</expan>.</ab>
</div>
<div type="cedula">
<ab>Cettula <expan>int<ex>er</ex>clusa</expan>: <expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns denn
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und gebetten habt von der lewff
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> czu Beheim etc., wissen wir zu disen
                                <expan>czeit<ex>en</ex></expan> niht
                            <expan>treffenlich<ex>er</ex></expan> meͣr. Wol sagt man bey uns, daz
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, der römisch etc. künig, auf dem Perg zun
                        Kutten sey und meyne <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> volk
                                <expan>zusame<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>bringe<ex>n</ex></expan> und ein velt zu machen. Ob aber das also sey
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> wie sich das machen
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan>, <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> wir noch
                        niht <expan>eygensch<ex>aft</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
